Plot: Delgo, an adventurous but naive teenager, must rally his group of friends to protect their world from conflict between the Lockni and Nohrin people.
Title: Delgo
Writer: Patrick J. Cowan (screenplay), Carl Dream (screenplay), Jennifer Jones-Mitchell (screenplay), Marc F. Adler (story), Scott Biear (story), Jason Maurer (story)
Actors: Freddie Prinze Jr., Chris Kattan, Jennifer Love Hewitt, Anne Bancroft
tomatoConsensus: Delgo features a blend of plot elements from earlier (and superior) fantasy films, with weaker animation and dull characters.
